inks are established between research artifacts - e.g.&nbsp; Zenodo metadata for a policy paper includes a link to a poster presented at a professional conference and course materials presented a workshop.</span></li>  <li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="2"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Instructions are provided for how to cite each component</span></li>  </ul>  </li>  </ul>  <p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', 4, 0, `templates`.`createdById`, `templates`.`created`, `templates`.`modifiedById`, `templates`.`modified` FROM `templates` WHERE `ownerId` = 'https://ror.org/02zv3m156' AND `name` = 'EHA Outputs Management Plan for Policy and Training Centric Projects');
